aa(lp47
VAnd that led to something which you probably do know.
p48
aVGuitar Hero came out of our lab,
p49
aVand my two teenage daughters and most of the students at the MIT Media Lab
p50
aVare proof that if you make the right kind of interface,
p51
aVpeople are really interested in being in the middle of a piece of music,
p52
aVand playing it over and over and over again.
