aa(lp54
VSo, the model works, but it's only the tip of the iceberg,
p55
aVbecause my second idea is that it's not enough just to want
p56
aVto make music in something like Guitar Hero.
p57
aVAnd music is very fun, but it's also transformative.
p58
aVIt's very, very important.
p59
aVMusic can change your life, more than almost anything.
p60
aVIt can change the way you communicate with others,
p61
aVit can change your body, it can change your mind. So, we're trying
p62
aVto go to the next step of how you build on top of something like Guitar Hero.
