aVWe are very involved in education. We have a long-term project
p64
aVcalled Toy Symphony, where we make all kinds of instruments that are also addictive,
p65
aVbut for little kids, so the kids will fall in love with making music,
p66
aVwant to spend their time doing it, and then will demand to know how it works,
p67
