p68
aVlike these Music Shapers that measure the electricity in your fingers,
p69
aVBeatbugs that let you tap in rhythms \u2014 they gather your rhythm,
p70
aVand like hot potato, you send your rhythm to your friends,
p71
aVwho then have to imitate or respond to what your doing \u2014
p72
aVand a software package called Hyperscore, which lets anybody use lines and color
p73
aVto make quite sophisticated music. Extremely easy to use, but once you use it,
p74
aVyou can go quite deep \u2014 music in any style. And then, by pressing a button,
p75
aVit turns into music notation so that live musicians can play your pieces.
