aVSo, one of the growing fields that we're working on
p83
aVat the Media Lab right now is music, mind and health.
p84
aVA lot of you have probably seen Oliver Sacks' wonderful new book called
p85
aV"Musicophilia". It's on sale in the bookstore. It's a great book.
p86
aVIf you haven't seen it, it's worth reading. He's a pianist himself,
p87
aVand he details his whole career of looking at and observing
p88
aVincredibly powerful effects that music has had on peoples' lives in unusual situations.
