p91
aVthat people with advanced Alzheimer's can still respond to.
p92
aVMaybe many of you have noticed this with loved ones,
p93
aVyou can find somebody who can't recognize their face in the mirror,
p94
aVor can't tell anyone in their family, but you can still find a shard of music
p95
aVthat that person will jump out of the chair and start singing. And with that
p96
aVyou can bring back parts of people's memories and personalities.
p97
aVMusic is the best way to restore speech to people who have lost it through strokes,
p98
aVmovement to people with Parkinson's disease.
p99
aVIt's very powerful for depression, schizophrenia, many, many things.
